sequenceDiagram
    participant P1 as Player 1
    participant Server as Server
    participant P2 as Player 2

    P1->>Server: JoinLobby
    P2->>Server: JoinLobby
    Server->>P1: LobbyUpdated
    Server->>P2: LobbyUpdated

    P1->>Server: StartGame
    Server->>P1: GameStarted
    Server->>P2: GameStarted

    loop Game Loop
        P1->>Server: UpdatePosition
        P2->>Server: UpdatePosition
        Server->>P1: StateUpdated
        Server->>P2: StateUpdated
    end

    Server->>P1: RoundEnded / GameEnded
    Server->>P2: RoundEnded / GameEnded
